   "author_association" : "CONTRIBUTOR",
   "body" : "The previous behavior, skipping some `DisconnectBlock()` calls at level 3, \r\nbut then attempting to reconnect these blocks at level 4, made `ConnectBlock()` assert   \r\nbecause the best block of the in-memory coins cache would not correspond to the added block's predecessor.\r\n\r\nThis can be tested with a small `dbcache` value, for example:\r\n`./bitcoind -signet -dbcache=10`\r\n`./bitcoin-cli -signet verifychain 4 1000`\r\n    \r\nFixes #25563",
